###

### Get Mapbox token (public function)
GET https://zfiexgjcuojodmnsinsz.functions.supabase.co/get-mapbox-token
Content-Type: application/json

### Generate QA test packet (public function)  
POST https://zfiexgjcuojodmnsinsz.functions.supabase.co/generate-test-packet
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### Get QA packet via API (public function)
GET https://zfiexgjcuojodmnsinsz.functions.supabase.co/qa-packet-api
Content-Type: application/json

### Check email domain (public function)
POST https://zfiexgjcuojodmnsinsz.functions.supabase.co/email-domain-check
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@university.edu"
}

### Enrich university info (public function)
POST https://zfiexgjcuojodmnsinsz.functions.supabase.co/university-info-enricher
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "university_name": "Technical University of Berlin",
  "city": "Berlin"
}

### Ingest universities data (requires authentication)
POST https://zfiexgjcuojodmnsinsz.functions.supabase.co/ingest-universities
Authorization: Bearer {JWT_TOKEN}
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### Setup QA users (requires authentication)
POST https://zfiexgjcuojodmnsinsz.functions.supabase.co/setup-qa-users
Authorization: Bearer {JWT_TOKEN}
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### TestSprite API integration (requires authentication)
POST https://zfiexgjcuojodmnsinsz.functions.supabase.co/testsprite-api
Authorization: Bearer {JWT_TOKEN}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "action": "create_test",
  "test_data": {
    "name": "University search test",
    "url": "https://universityassist25.lovable.app/search",
    "description": "Test search functionality"
  }
}